00:22:30,480 --> 00:22:32,240
The day you brought Duk-su here?

278
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:34,680
Your mother was crying inside,

279
00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:36,520
and I'd stepped out first.

280
00:22:36,520 --> 00:22:38,720
Then I found this stone on the ground.

281
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:43,040
So I picked it up, almost in a trance, and??

282
00:22:43,040 --> 00:22:45,480
It was warm.

283
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:47,080
Just like Duk-su's hands.

284
00:22:49,960 --> 00:22:54,200
So I held onto it tight like I was holding Duk-su's hand,

285
00:22:54,200 --> 00:22:56,120
and brought it home.

286
00:22:57,400 --> 00:23:00,360
So that's why??

287
00:23:02,560 --> 00:23:05,320
And ever since then, I've been all over the country

288
00:23:05,320 --> 00:23:08,240
looking for rocks like a madman.

289
00:23:11,680 --> 00:23:14,120
To help Duk-su make some friends?

290
00:23:14,120 --> 00:23:15,000
Friends?

291
00:23:17,080 --> 00:23:18,400
Is that what they'd be?

292
00:23:21,320 --> 00:23:23,840
Can I  hold his hand, too?

293
00:23:23,840 --> 00:23:25,120
Of course! Here.

294
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:30,560
It really is warm.

295
00:23:30,560 --> 00:23:31,960
Duk-su's hand, I mean.

296
00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:47,280
Mom.

297
00:23:47,280 --> 00:23:50,360
Once my CD matures, should we live together?

298
00:23:50,360 --> 00:23:51,960
What's got into you all of a sudden?

