417
00:34:04,320 --> 00:34:06,160
Are you going somewhere?

418
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:08,480
Oh, I'm going back to New York.

419
00:34:09,640 --> 00:34:12,760
I had a purpose in coming here??

420
00:34:20,600 --> 00:34:22,880
- To get over my slump. - Oh!

