484
00:38:18,120 --> 00:38:19,120
Or??

485
00:38:19,120 --> 00:38:22,000
How about you open a judo center in New York?

486
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:26,080
Wouldn't it be faster for you to open an art academy in Korea?

